{"word":"H2498 - חָלַף - châlaph - khaw-laf' - Abolish","slug":"H2498","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָלַף</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>châlaph"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khaw-laf'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Abolish"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D7;&#x05DC;&#x05E3; - cha&#x0302;laph</b> - <i>khaw-laf'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>slide</i> by, that is, (by implication) to <i>hasten</i> away, <i>pass</i> on, <i>spring</i> up, <i>pierce</i> or <i>change: - </i>abolish, alter change, cut off, go on forward, grow up, be over, pass (away, on, through), renew, sprout, strike through."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2475\">H2475</a>, <a href=\"#/H2487\">H2487</a>, <a href=\"#/H2500\">H2500</a>, <a href=\"#/H2501\">H2501</a>, <a href=\"#/H4252\">H4252</a>, <a href=\"#/H4253\">H4253</a>"}]}